# System Design Diagrams — Learning Lifecycle App

---

## 1. Overall System Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Client["🖥️ Browser (Next.js App)"]
        UI[React Pages & Components]
        SC[shadcn/ui + Tailwind CSS]
        RC[recharts - Analytics]
    end

    subgraph Server["⚙️ Next.js Server"]
        API[Route Handlers - /api/...]
        ML[Mongoose Models]
        AL[AI Layer]
        SL[Streak & Achievement Logic]
    end

    subgraph DB["🍃 MongoDB Atlas"]
        US[(users)]
        SU[(subjects)]
        CU[(curricula)]
        LS[(learning_sessions)]
    end

    subgraph External["🌐 External Services"]
        AI[OpenAI / Gemini API]
    end

    UI -->|fetch| API
    API --> ML
    API --> SL
    API --> AL
    ML --> DB
    AL -->|prompt| AI
    AI -->|JSON topics| AL
```

---

## 2. MongoDB Data Model (ERD)

```mermaid
erDiagram
    USER {
        ObjectId _id
        string name
        string email
        int dailyGoalMinutes
        int currentStreak
        int longestStreak
        int totalMinutesLearned
        Date lastActiveDate
        string[] achievements
    }

    SUBJECT {
        ObjectId _id
        ObjectId userId
        string title
        string icon
        string color
        string skillLevel
        string[] tags
        int totalTopics
        int completedTopics
        int totalMinutesSpent
        Date lastStudiedAt
    }

    CURRICULUM {
        ObjectId _id
        ObjectId subjectId
        ObjectId userId
        bool aiGenerated
    }

    TOPIC {
        ObjectId _id
        string title
        string description
        int order
        string status
        int estimatedMinutes
        int actualMinutes
        string notes
        Date completedAt
    }

    LEARNING_SESSION {
        ObjectId _id
        ObjectId userId
        ObjectId subjectId
        ObjectId topicId
        int durationMinutes
        string notes
        string mood
        Date sessionDate
    }

    USER ||--o{ SUBJECT : "has many"
    USER ||--o{ LEARNING_SESSION : "logs many"
    SUBJECT ||--|| CURRICULUM : "has one"
    CURRICULUM ||--o{ TOPIC : "contains many"
    LEARNING_SESSION }o--|| SUBJECT : "belongs to"
    LEARNING_SESSION }o--|| TOPIC : "targets"
```

---

## 3. User Journey Flow

```mermaid
journey
    title A User's Daily Learning Lifecycle
    section Plan
      Create a Subject: 5: User
      Generate Curriculum with AI: 4: User, AI
      Review & Edit Topics: 3: User
    section Learn
      Open Daily Dashboard: 5: User
      Pick a Topic to Study: 4: User
      Start Timed Session: 5: User
      Take Notes & Browse Resources: 4: User
      End Session & Log Mood: 5: User
    section Track
      View Streak Updated: 5: System
      Check Daily Goal Ring: 4: User
      Browse Progress Charts: 3: User
    section Grow
      Unlock Achievement Badge: 5: System
      Review Heatmap History: 4: User
      Level Up Subject Skill: 3: User
```

