## 5. Learning Session — State Machine

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle : Open /learn page

    Idle --> TopicSelected : User picks a topic
    TopicSelected --> Running : Press "Start Session"

    Running --> Paused : Press Pause
    Paused --> Running : Press Resume

    Running --> Reviewing : Press "End Session"
    Paused --> Reviewing : Press "End Session"

    Reviewing --> Saved : Fill mood + notes → Submit
    Saved --> [*] : Redirects to Dashboard

    Saved --> StreakUpdated : Server checks last active date
    StreakUpdated --> GoalChecked : Compare today's total vs dailyGoal
    GoalChecked --> AchievementCheck : Check unlock conditions
    AchievementCheck --> [*]
```

---

## 6. API Layer Structure

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph "API Routes — /app/api/"
        S1["POST /subjects\nCreate subject"]
        S2["GET /subjects\nList all subjects"]
        S3["GET /subjects/:id\nGet subject detail"]
        S4["PUT /subjects/:id\nUpdate subject"]
        T1["POST /subjects/:id/topics\nAdd topic"]
        T2["PATCH /subjects/:id/topics/:topicId\nUpdate status / notes"]
        SE1["POST /sessions\nLog learning session"]
        SE2["GET /sessions\nList user sessions"]
        P1["GET /progress\nAggregated stats"]
        AI1["POST /generate\nAI curriculum generation"]
    end

    subgraph "Triggered Side Effects"
        ST1["Update streak & lastActiveDate"]
        ST2["Check & unlock achievements"]
        ST3["Update subject totalMinutesSpent"]
        ST4["Increment completedTopics count"]
    end

    SE1 --> ST1
    SE1 --> ST2
    SE1 --> ST3
    T2 --> ST4
    T2 --> ST2
```

---

## 7. Streak Logic

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["User ends learning session"] --> B["Save LearningSession to DB"]
    B --> C{"lastActiveDate == today?"}
    C -->|Yes| D["No streak change\nalready studied today"]
    C -->|No| E{"lastActiveDate == yesterday?"}
    E -->|Yes| F["currentStreak += 1\nUpdate longestStreak if needed"]
    E -->|No| G["currentStreak = 1\nStreak broken — reset"]
    F --> H["Save lastActiveDate = today"]
    G --> H
    D --> H
    H --> I["Check achievements\ne.g. 7-day streak badge"]
    I --> J["Return updated user stats to client"]
```

---

## 8. AI Curriculum Generation Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Page as /generate page
    participant API as /api/generate
    participant AI as OpenAI/Gemini

    User->>Page: Enter subject + skill level + keywords
    Page->>API: POST { title, skillLevel, keywords }
    API->>AI: Send structured prompt
    AI-->>API: Return JSON array of topics
    API-->>Page: Return generated curriculum
    Page->>User: Show preview (editable list of topics)
    User->>Page: Edit / reorder / remove topics
    User->>Page: Click "Save Curriculum"
    Page->>API: POST /api/subjects/:id/curriculum
    API-->>Page: Curriculum saved ✅
    Page->>User: Redirect to /subjects/:id
```
